{"tid":824953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日番工屌撚到個90後喊","createTime":"2018-09-17T09:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T16:57:42.000Z","uid":158407,"like":13,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5f13f7d9992de3272f6112f874adfff6b74b8457","tid":824953,"uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"話說今朝番工個90後遲左半個鐘，作為公司老屎忽咁就緊係幫口屌佢兩句話佢遲到。之後佢燥燥地咁講話琴日十號波今日好多人好多車，已經早左半個鐘頭出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢比經理叫左入佢房，我跟埋入去扮比野經理然後係側邊加鹽加醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個90後喊晒口好撚無辜咁話可唔可以比次機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最後仲說服經理出左封warning letter比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到去我仲屌佢話&rdquo;又唔見我會遲？家下d 90後真係垃山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &rdquo; 見到佢喊晒口咁沖左入左廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：住公司附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8a5143f1273a0512e362b4e54208464cdd3d4a","tid":824953,"uid":125213,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"ching型爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲90後唔吊唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517a339c9d3c9ad87a7d6f4d2d6d01f90523acc5","tid":824953,"uid":64564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"e59caa135460e1506cc397250793a562952dad17","tid":824953,"uid":18310,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"垃山是什麼？"},{"pid":"48f72216b39aea253d69a8887e1e894f3ce6fee9","tid":824953,"uid":111768,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"連登膠post越來越多..低能仔數量亦越來越多"},{"pid":"217ddf6f0b1396fc903879428f4901c4d1d729fc","tid":824953,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"3e3acc2f75651b9c54cb6c0ec3f9e3229e7569d2","tid":824953,"uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8a5143f1273a0512e362b4e54208464cdd3d4a","tid":824953,"uid":125213,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"ching型爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲90後唔吊唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"岩牙，屌撚到佢地仆街！"},{"pid":"fc14cb3f771a5d4625cd17919b37d7bf63b59531","tid":824953,"uid":168924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"出依啲垃圾po既意義係咩 <br />\n博負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ef01ff5f2f7417800277e75e1bcf51fb935d47","tid":824953,"uid":11512,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>比組爸中出左好後悔。。<br />\n</strong><br />\n#1<br />\n非洲族長（再生）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2018年8月23日 23:01:18<br />\n話說小妹今年第一年玩Ocamp，本身男朋友極度不滿話d組爸係獸父，去親10個有9個都會失身。<br />\n個時無理到佢，心諗我有男朋友佢地都唔會點亂黎，純粹去識下group mate咁樣<br />\n<br />\n點知其中一個組爸全程都好照顧我，雖然我一早已經話左比佢聽我有男朋友，佢話&lsquo;照顧仔女係爸爸責任&rsquo;個時聽完覺得佢應該唔係咩壞人就放心跟佢去玩。<br />\n<br />\n之後琴晚同男朋友嘈ocamp 野加上成班都飲大左，組爸送左我去佢個hall到。個時真係好感動，覺得終於都有人咁照顧我，然後大家開始攬攬錫錫上黎比佢中出埋.... 個時諗其實都無乜所謂佢呢幾日照顧得我咁辛苦。<br />\n今朝訓醒好後悔，好對唔住男朋友....同左男朋友幾年都未比佢搞過，組爸識左幾日就中出左...<br />\n究竟我應唔應該同男朋友坦白好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>外母反對我同男朋友一齊結婚。。</strong><br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n非洲族長（再生）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2018年8月13日 11:43:34<br />\n同男朋友一齊左六年以上，中五已經一齊左，最近諗住同男朋友移民澳洲結婚，同左未來外母食左餐飯同佢講晒我地結婚計劃，因為已經儲左筆錢諗住係個邊開餐廳。點知外母極力反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話咩點解要搬去咁遠，又話咩我地個時中學讀慈幻已經覺得我好無禮貌，一直都唔想我同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成餐飯食得勁唔開心面阻阻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下巴打係咪真係無機會。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同男朋友坦白點知佢介意我唔係處。。</strong><br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n非洲族長（再生）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2018年7月6日 21:18:30<br />\n同左男朋友2個月，佢份人比較怕羞，一直都未同佢搞過野<br />\n琴日同佢錫到興起，我準備幫佢戴套個時佢問我點解咁熟手<br />\n我唔想呃佢坦白話佢知我同幾個EX咩都玩過晒（SM，屎眼，制服）<br />\n佢即刻推開左我話仲未準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢咁保守，諗住同佢坦白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 21世紀仲邊個介意條女係咪處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地話啦我咁樣岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍施緊係要坦白，佢慢慢會明白<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食臭雞比人開發晒仲懶有道理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>EX打黎話大左肚。。</strong><br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n非洲族長（再生）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2018年6月19日 06:06:42<br />\n早排同左ex分身，大家意見唔夾<br />\n到早幾日佢搵番我以為可以再一齊返<br />\n點知佢同我講佢一個月冇嚟M，用驗孕棒驗左有BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇撚到我即刻收線。<br />\n同左屋企人講比屋企人屌到仆街，而家離家出走<br />\n想問下ching邊到有地方租平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：hku year1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無乜經濟能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同其中一個港男仆過野 你問我盡答</strong><br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n非洲族長（再生）<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2018年5月5日 01:31:50<br />\n唔會開名，自爆唔答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當故仔聽又好，自己發揮想像力，或者套入任何一位都好。請出招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21ffc14bfc47760ee18559b264b5fdc19226cf","tid":824953,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daba73f976e3e01207fd3f4403108b65583dda8e","tid":824953,"uid":175732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"歡迎黎到連登關愛台"},{"pid":"934f42989d2ca137d27e74792373f1256b895f38","tid":824953,"uid":71508,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"算啦此post已完 <br />\n起完樓主底 <br />\n樓主應該係現實生活中無乜朋友果類人 <br />\n然後慘到要上黎連登呃負評博存在感 <br />\n大家不要再留言了<br />\n假膠撚"},{"pid":"8ff2814062961de20ada4d23cdf4b29f03358e28","tid":824953,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"下次唔好咁啦<br />\n如果遇著個個係我你應該入左廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16722b917bc3cee3299a0ca04e9e97d1689ddbb5","tid":824953,"uid":332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff2814062961de20ada4d23cdf4b29f03358e28","tid":824953,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"下次唔好咁啦<br />\n如果遇著個個係我你應該入左廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"但你去左坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7868901d19a3737706770cccff00d5098449332e","tid":824953,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e59caa135460e1506cc397250793a562952dad17",